ss=\"reviewer-name\">cyberdym</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We recently purchased Kali Forms Pro. The Team at Kali Forms were incredibly helpful and provided very timely support. Very pleasant to deal with; very knowledgeable; fully recommend!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin I love it.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sexmagic14\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b6fd978010d17fd9b6e738e8c0887f36?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b6fd978010d17fd9b6e738e8c0887f36?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sexmagic14\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sexmagic14</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin I love it.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juliensybille\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/ab8476b6ad085ef45f85d5d5f696f992?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/ab8476b6ad085ef45f85d5d5f696f992?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/juliensybille\" class=\"reviewer-name\">juliensybille</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 24, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great plugin, simple to used</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very helpful support and gorgeous product!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dsedlarski\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/67a546bf5d096ae024d8576034480e73?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/67a546bf5d096ae024d8576034480e73?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dsedlarski\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dsedlarski</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 11, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hi there!\nTwo months ago I\'ve tried this plugin. It looks better than other and it\'s very easy to work with. I had some very difficult needs with the attachment field and the support team helped me with a lot. They was so dedicated to the problem and now I can use the plugin with no problems!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muy buen complemento</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ivanhdez73\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/200a6ffa29979d84663aa0ccbc4dadea?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/200a6ffa29979d84663aa0ccbc4dadea?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ivanhdez73\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ivanhdez73</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 6, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Muy buen complemento, aunque un poco confuso</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin and interface</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/petredobrescu\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e02690fe409080c285f400f31265ca01?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e02690fe409080c285f400f31265ca01?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/petredobrescu\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Pedro <small>(petredobrescu)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple and fast and after you get used to the interface, it proves great!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Free version is average</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/clayray\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e557660fd1785dde3469137d12e31d1d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e557660fd1785dde3469137d12e31d1d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/clayray\" class=\"reviewer-name\">clayray</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 29, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The free version is certainly not very good advertising for the Pro version.\nThe default styling of the forms is terrible. Field widths cannot be adjusted, so in a contact form the First Name and Last Name fields awkwardly overhang each other instead of (for example) taking up 50% of the available width.\nThe form editor is somewhat counter intuitive (especially in this era of WYSIWYG editors), and there seemed to be no way to return from the (full page width) form editor back to the WP admin back end without having to type the wp-admin URL back into the browser address bar. Although I worked out later that I could click the X at the top right of the editor to achieve the same effect.\nWas previously using the Divi contact form module, and have just discovered that it now supports Google ReCaptcha, which is the only reason I came here for.\nMost people will just want a contact form from this plugin, and for this the lite version is very unattractive, and the Pro version overpriced.\nAlso, for a plugin called Kali Forms, I would expect it to appear in my plugins list under the letter K. Instead, the title in the plugins list is \"WordPress Forms Made Easy - Kali Forms\", which means it appears last in the list. A somewhat counter-intuitive sales pitch, made after the plugin has already been downloaded.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does not work</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/meister1\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/f6eb694d1c25b6a74c4a5b9e03c561f0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/f6eb694d1c25b6a74c4a5b9e03c561f0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/meister1\" class=\"reviewer-name\">meister1</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I installed it, could not get emails, tried all troubleshooting options still not working, </div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:159:\"Kali Forms is the most powerful &amp; user-friendly WordPress form plugin. Easily add contact forms, payment forms, feedback forms and more to your we &hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/kali-forms.1.6.5.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:0:{}s:8:\"versions\";a:22:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/kali-forms.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/kali-forms.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/kali-forms.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/kali-forms.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:59: