anagement</strong></li>\n     <li>  Easy to use and customize </li>\n     <li>\n<strong>Fully responsive </strong> with  <strong>Retina ready</strong> : Beautifully display your website with any device. </li>\n     <li><strong>Mobile Support  </strong></li>\n     <li> Highly  <strong>SEO optimization</strong>\n</li>\n     <li>\n<strong>Faster loading</strong>  with ultra speed </li>\n     <li>\n<strong>Google Font </strong> support: It&#8217;s your choice to select between 600+ Google Fonts </li>\n     <li>\n<strong>1200+ icons</strong>  with medical icons </li>\n     <li> Unlimited colour options </li>\n     <li><strong>One click installer</strong></li>\n     <li> Translation ready </li>\n     <li>5 Star Customer Support</li>\n     <li>\n<strong>One-time payment </strong> with  <strong>Lifetime update</strong>  and  <strong>usage</strong>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>CHANGELOG</strong></p>\n<p>Ivy School WordPress Theme 1.3.2 &#8211; 2019-08-27</p>\n<pre>Update\n- Added edit lesson in LearnPress.\n- Fixed page tag course LearnPress not working.\n- Fixed z-index Slider Revolution.\n- Updated file language theme.</pre>\n<p>Ivy School WordPress Theme 1.3.1 &#8211; 2019-04-24</p>\n<pre>+ Optimized installation package.\n+ Fixed outdate template in Woocommerce.</pre>\n<p>Ivy School WordPress Theme 1.3.0 &#8211; 2019-03-29</p>\n<pre>+ Updated widget cart.\n+ Improved social share option.\n+ Improved layout option.\n+ Improved event datetime format.\n+ Updated register on checkout page.\n+ Updated setting display option for single page.</pre>\n<p>Ivy School WordPress Theme 1.2.0 &#8211; 2019-02-14</p>\n<pre>- Supported Gutenberg.\n- Improved translation file.</pre>\n<p>Ivy School WordPress Theme 1.1 &#8211; 2019/01/29</p>\n<pre>- Included new Driving demo.\n- Fixed some minor bugs (Responsive, WooCommerce).\n</pre>\n<p>Ivy School WordPress Theme 1.0.6 &#8211; 2019/01/24</p>\n<pre>- Add option login/logout/register redirect.\n- Improved some problems in customize.\n- Fixed so